title: Eerie Archives Vol 1-10
description:
Volumes 1-10 of 'Eerie Archives'

Dark Horse Archives, 2009-2012, 2733 total pages 

Vol. 1, issues 1-5, 258 pages
Vol. 2, issues 6-10, 290 pages
Vol. 3, issues 11-15, 258 pages
Vol. 4, issues 16-22, 255 pages
Vol. 5, issues 23-27, 274 pages
Vol. 6, issues 28-31, 248 pages
Vol. 7, issues 32-36, 290 pages
Vol. 8, issues 37-41, 314 pages 
Vol. 9, issues 42-46, 274 pages
Vol. 10, issues 47-51, 272 pages

The list of contributors on these books is just bonkers. Selecting just a few of the biggest and best known gives you names like Gene Colan, Frank Frazetta, Steve Ditko, Alex Toth, Al Williamson, Wallace Wood, Archie Goodwin, Ernie Colon, Mike Ploog, Dave Cockrum, Doug Moench and Richard Corben, but there are SO MANY more than that. Absolutely classic works, presented beautifully. Not really much more to say than that.
